# Docusaurus Conventions

## Structure
- `website/docs/` is the docs root; `intro.md` with `slug: /` is the home page
- New pages: add `.md` in the appropriate folder; sidebar is autogenerated
- Use `_category_.json` in folders for labels and ordering

## Configuration
- `website/docusaurus.config.ts` — site title, theme, Mermaid, etc.
- `website/sidebars.ts` — sidebar config (autogenerated from docs structure)

## Links
- Use relative file paths with `.md` extension: `[Text](path/to/doc.md)`
- Cross-folder: `[Setup](../setup/cursor-setup.md)`

## Mermaid Diagrams
Use fenced code blocks with `mermaid` language tag.

## Local Preview
```bash
cd website && npm run start
```

## Build
```bash
cd website && npm run build
```
